text: Viktória Szabó (born 26 May 1997) is a Hungarian football midfielder who plays for German club 1. FC Saarbrücken and the Hungary national team. ==Club career== In July 2016 Szabó joined 2. Bundesliga club Saarbrücken from 1. FC Lübars. ==International career== At the 2016 Cyprus Cup, Szabó scored Hungary's winning goal against the Republic of Ireland from a direct free kick. ==References== ==External links== * * Profile at 1.
